history.content:
Hey everyone,
This semester HKN is offering tutoring services weekly on Monday through Friday 11 AM to 3 PM and 8 PM to 10 PM (to accommodate different time zones). Similar to some of the lower division classes, we will have an office hours queue website where students can submit tickets for help with classes, conceptual problems, or homeworks (not projects). Additionally classmates and friends can submit group tickets to review concepts together.All the information related to HKN's tutoring hours can be found at hkn.mu/tutor and the link for the office hour queue is at hkn.mu/ohqueue.Thanks,
Tutoring Committee
Eta Kappa Nu
